EGIFTER  Trademark Information
 GroupGifting.com, Inc.
Promotional services, namely, promoting the goods of others by means of providing online gift cards and special offers; Promoting the goods and services of others by providing an interactive website where users can purchase electronic gift cards through mobile devices, web sites and social networks including providing users to chip in for one electronic gift card to a specific recipient; Advertising services, namely, promoting the gift cards a...
Software as a service (SaaS) services featuring software for companies to market and sell their electronic gift cards through mobile devices, web sites and social networks, including giving these companies the ability to offer group gifting where multiple people can chip in for one electronic gift card to a specific recipient and also allow them to make special offers to their customers




Perfect for these industries

Advertising,  Business & Retail Services
Computer & Software Services & Scientific Services





