Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of GroupGifting.com, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
GroupGifting.com, Inc., doing business as eGifter, Inc., operates an online platform that provides social and mobile gifting solutions. It provides a social gift giving service that allows users to send free and paid gift cards to friends and family. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Huntington, New York.


315 Main Street2nd FloorHuntington, NY 11743United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 516-882-1200

Fax: 631-501-3526

www.egifter.com







