GroupGifting.com, Inc. Key Developments

eGifter Launches Enhanced Group Gifting Platform
Dec 6 16
eGifter announced the launch of an enhanced group gifting platform.  This next generation technology allows gift givers to collect and to give generous, thoughtful gifts for a wide variety of gifting occasions with ease and convenience.  Say goodbye to IOUs and stressing over what to gift the recipient. eGifter knows that shoppers and recipients alike would rather receive a gift card more than anything else on their list, and have always supported bringing people together to give gift cards.  All eGifter cards are digital and delivered electronically.  Groups can seamlessly collect money and provide recipients with the incredible gift of choice from hundreds of gift cards from almost every major brand in the U.S. There is something for everyone on every occasion. When the gift is delivered with all the personal messages, the recipient can choose from hundreds of gift cards using the eGifter website or mobile app. Key features include: Organize gifts with one or multiple recipients, Personalize the gift experience by uploading photos, videos and custom messages, A unique gifting page to track the gift's progress, Give the gift of choice so the recipient can choose from hundreds of popular gift cards, FREE for the buyers and recipients – and no service fees!.


